HEADWORD: malthusian theory
<hw>malthusian theory</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Malthus' theory that
population increase would outpace increases in the means of subsistence;
Malthusianism. See <er>Malthusian</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
